{
  "stem": "444.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And from then on, I was quite-- not often, but every few days, I was in their home, talking with-- with their father.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, they had-- they had their problems, and we talked about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one day, I had to send Jews out to work, but they were always late.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Instead of being there at 8 or 9 o'clock, they were there at 1 o'clock, 12 o'clock, so they arrested me for sabotage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was arrested by-- by an officer or two officers from the army-- from air forces, pardon me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a few soldiers [INAUDIBLE] were parading me through the village where the airfield was built.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was, at that time, at the airfield.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they put me in-- in a jail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was there for two or three days, but I got out because my-- my superiors needed me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They wanted me to become a German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They gave me all kinds of propositions and promises.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They would send me to-- to-- College of the Luftwaffe engineers, that means engineers for the-- for the air forces.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I told that fellow, who was a very, very fine guy-- Yenkner was his name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The guy-- as a matter of fact, that was speaking to Hitler once in while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he told me that I-- made me all the promises of what they were going to do for me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have a big opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I told him, unfortunately, I said, but I have to declare myself as a German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, there again, the situation-- I told him that I cannot do it because I'm Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one moment, he still tried to persuade me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked him, what would you do in my place?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
